Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.35,0:00:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,溺於蠱惑之悲緣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.81,0:00:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,夢境或現實 光或暗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.38,0:00:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,言語無盡 一顯一消
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.34,0:00:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,搖曳於光陰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.95,0:00:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,眾說紛紜是宵伽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.72,0:00:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,難消之怨 願為消之
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.55,0:01:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多該來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.37,0:01:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,菊理 你為什麼要點拉麵的外賣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.33,0:01:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,這個嘛 有些緣由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:02:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,她這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.61,0:02:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你屁股癢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.26,0:02:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係 撓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.44,0:02:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,蠢貨 才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.86,0:02:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.09,0:02:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:12.69,pm1,,0,0,0,,{\frz267.6\pos(1036,216)}超 像
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.12,0:02:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,數目正好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.06,0:02:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,菊理 你這是對他愛得火熱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,才 才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,還有 你這話也太老套了 眼珠子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好燙 燙燙燙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你是說拉麵很火熱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.33,0:02:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你也有可愛的時候嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,深藏的愛慕之心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.96,0:02:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我記得曾經發生過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這種純粹的愛慕引發的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:51.98,zhu,,0,0,0,,鹼性乾電池
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.43,0:02:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在你體內
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.25,0:03:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.68,0:03:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嚇到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,秋惠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:22.05,biaoti,,0,0,0,,籠中鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼無精打采的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你還很在意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.05,0:03:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,逸子的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.16,0:03:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你不要太在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是逸子自尊心太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.04,0:03:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然沒想到她會轉學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.05,0:03:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟丹下老師的事情鬧得那麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,她肯定是不好意思待在學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,丹下老師到底去哪裡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然我的小夥伴們說他是跟人私奔了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但那肯定不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,因為丹下老師怎麼看都…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 我有點急事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 柚木
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.65,0:04:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安 阿明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,阿明？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:35.58,zhu,,0,0,0,,山岡電器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那我先掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,客人還在等著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.84,0:04:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,總是讓你等這麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:05:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,賣完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,五號電池行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你昨天和前天都是買的五號吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 我多嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,47日元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,因為很多地方都需要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,也對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.71,0:05:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,錢不夠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.37,0:05:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,還差多少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,46日元 差1日元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那就便宜賣給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你都是常客了 給你優惠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.59,0:05:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,暖暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.16,0:06:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子錢不夠…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,別發出這麼大聲音 蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,會被鄰居聽到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你對那小鬼拋了不少媚眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 美津子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,從什麼時候開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的 不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,下次再來就把他趕走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 他是客人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是客人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,回答呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:06:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:13.58,zhu,,0,0,0,,君之怨恨 願為消之
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫什麼名字來著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,阿明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.96,0:07:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,您好 這裡是山岡電器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,看來你乖乖待在店裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:07:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,客人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,今天還沒人來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我會再打來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.30,0:08:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫誠次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,御景合格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.60,0:08:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,表情不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,還好你知道地獄少女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.77,0:08:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,有怨恨的人就跟我們說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我們地獄少年隊會送詛咒用的稻草人給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.16,0:08:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有必要這麼生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,去死一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.69,0:09:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,再問你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,三點多的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,接電話那麼慢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我說了我在收衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,少騙人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你把那個小鬼叫來了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的是在收衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,給我說實話 美津子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,給我等著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:09:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,地 地獄少女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.35,0:10:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊 小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,輪入道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.56,0:10:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,請收下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你若真的想消除怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.06,0:10:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,將這根紅線解開即可
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦解開紅線 便正式與我締結了契約
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你怨恨之人將立刻墜入地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,怨恨若已消除 你自身亦將付出代價
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,害人終害己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,締結契約之後 你的靈魂也將墜入地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不過那是在你死之後了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.74,0:10:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我也會下地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,之後就由你自己抉擇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼… 要給我看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.43,0:11:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼 地獄少女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,能耽誤你一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.41,0:11:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我有事情想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.45,0:11:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是朋友找我商量的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 有多喜歡那個人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.57,0:11:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.60,0:11:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:12:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,想拯救被欺凌的女人 這種心情我倒是能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.15,0:12:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是真心喜歡的 我朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.69,0:12:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,果然還是得想辦法解決那個壞男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.68,0:12:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,想什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.27,0:12:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那個女人討厭那個男人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,當然討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,每天都被虐待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.84,0:12:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那她為什麼不逃跑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,因為逃不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,即使逃跑了 也會被抓回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,然後虐待會變本加厲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那個男人就是這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然我沒見過他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.84,0:12:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但我覺得應該是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,阿明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.55,0:12:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那個女人是怎麼看待你朋友的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.97,0:13:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,她說過喜歡他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,阿明 跟你的朋友說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.19,0:13:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,讓他最好別再和這件事扯上關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然我也說不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.21,0:13:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但喜歡有很多種形式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.35,0:13:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那個女人大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,她…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,她是想逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,阿明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.23,0:13:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,小姐為什麼要執著於她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,憑感覺的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.06,0:13:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.83,0:13:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這可說不定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.99,0:13:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,也可能是想拿她當宿主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,比起蝴蝶的形態 變成人類行動更方便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有實體 就只能寄宿於其他人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 答案總有一天會揭曉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,再觀望一段時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.73,0:14:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這個城市
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,還要再發生令人生厭的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.69,0:14:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是 是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,討厭 別嚇我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.11,0:14:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用去學校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒到放學的時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是學校裡發生了不愉快的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,翹課可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好了好了 快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.79,0:15:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,這是繩索留下的痕跡對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.09,0:15:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,別接那傢伙的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,待在那種人身邊不會有好結果的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.49,0:15:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,掛斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.70,0:15:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,逃跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,沒必要和那種人在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,現在立刻逃跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你沒地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.91,0:16:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,可以來我家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我會和父母解釋的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,對 來我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你來就是為了這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,翹課過來就為了說這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.68,0:16:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那就跟我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你走吧 他就快回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,被他看到就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.25,0:16:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 你和我一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.25,0:16:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.29,0:16:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 是我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,所以請冷靜…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你果然勾引他了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,快點…逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.87,0:17:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你勾引他了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.19,0:17:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是 說話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你的靈魂也將墜入地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.26,0:17:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.33,0:17:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,怨恨已聞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.85,0:19:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.46,0:19:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,這是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.74,0:19:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.52,0:19:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,清爽多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,身體好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.23,0:19:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.31,0:19:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,菊理要香腸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,今天真熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.78,0:19:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你們用電過度了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,微波爐沒插電啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.77,0:19:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉 插頭在老爹手上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.57,0:19:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,要插囉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.40,0:19:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.89,0:19:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.90,0:20:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑 我做了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是虐待你老婆了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.61,0:20:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒虐待她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我是在保護她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你說那叫保護？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.12,0:20:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,她…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,為了她 我的老婆 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.54,0:20:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他是這麼說的 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不能再插了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.76,0:20:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,迷失於黑暗的可悲之影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.09,0:20:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,傷害 蔑視他人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.47,0:20:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,沉溺於罪惡的孽魂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.11,0:20:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,死一次如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,要節約用電哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.37,0:21:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,電話 要給她打電話才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,借我電話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.47,0:21:14.40,zhu,,0,0,0,,你聽見了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.57,0:21:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,此怨此恨 將流向地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.32,0:21:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.82,0:21:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,明天再來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.94,0:21:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,明天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.84,0:21:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我早上去學校之前過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.60,0:21:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.74,0:21:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.83,0:22:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,第二天早上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.53,0:22:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,電器店的老闆娘失蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.66,0:22:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,君之怨恨 願為消之
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.59,0:22:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,
